id: pm-1kxs
title: "As a coding agent, I can discover and operate every pm capability from a one-screen top-level command list without out-of-band context"
description: "Agent-story capability statement for the CLI simplification epic pm-n7rr. Delivered when the consolidated noun-verb surface ships: the agent reads pm --help (~15 nouns), drills into a noun for its verbs, and never needs to guess among sibling top-level spellings. Duplicate check: 12-epic agent-story layer covers capability epics; none covers the simplification initiative."
